summary: Marvel Zombies RP Wanted Connection: Miles Morales Requested by: Peter Parker Telephone networks have failed, the internet is...
caption:
Marvel Zombies RP Wanted Connection: Miles Morales
Requested by: Peter Parker

Telephone networks have failed, the internet is gone.  Modern communication seems to have come to an end.  What remains is radiowaves.  People with the right equipment have begun to communicate with anyone in range using CB radios, walkie talkies, whatever they can get their hands on.  Some are broadcasting, some are just listening.

As he tuned the radio through the various channels, looking for news, Miles heard the end of a series of coordinates.  As the static cleared, a familiar voice sounded, a voice he had not heard in over a year –

This is Peter Parker broadcasting for Miles Morales. I know you are a survivor so you are out there somewhere. This is no city, but its got video games, good people, strong walls and plenty to eat. Also hot showers are a thing here so yeah try to find your way here kid. Us spiders need to stick together.

Marvel Zombies RP is a Marvel Comics AU roleplay established 1 April 2017. We look forward to surviving with you.

body:
( scenarios )

[ Takes place during Inifinity War ]

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Y/n: You four! Come quick, something’s going on outside.

Stephen: I’m sorry, who is she again?

Tony: Just one of the many ex- villains that we saved from the darkness. Oh and, an ex fling of a friend. Come on!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter turns around seeing Y/n fly into the air towards the space ship, only for her to be thrown back by a force seconds later.

Peter: Hey Ned, I need you to cause a distraction!

Ned:

Ned: Oh shit, there’s that new hero! She’s kinda hot.. Hey, how old do you think she is?

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter saving you, to then only regret it..

Y/n: Thanks for that, Parker, but I had it all under control.

Peter: Well it didn’t seem like you did. You’re lucky I even showed up.

Y/n: You shouldn’t go. It’s dangerous for a little freshmen like you to be there!

Peter: You know what? I was actually quite terrified of what might happen once I get there, but now I think I just have more motivation to kick some ass. Ugh, you’re so -

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Y/n trying to look out for Peter -

Y/n looked behind her to see how high she’s gone up.

Y/n: Peter! What are you doing here?

Peter: I’m here to help save the world *grunt* obviously!

Before Peter could reach her, Y/n was quick to kick him harshly, sending him falling right back down.

Peter: WHAT WAS THAT FOR?!

Y/n: Sorry Spidey, Iron Man’s orders! We can’t have a teenager’s life in our hands.

Peter: STOP ACTING LIKE I’M THE ONLY YOUNG HERO HERE! YOU’RE ONLY OLDER BY A YEAR!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter trying to give reasons to dislike Y/n -

Peter: You shouldn’t trust her, she’ll only break your heart in unfortunate ways. And she was once one of the bad guys so -

Stephen: You’re the one who had the fling.

Peter: What? How’d you know that?

Stephen: Your metal friend over there.

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Saving Y/n Pt .2 -

Thanos throws you a big hit sending you flying to the air.

Y/n: PLEASE LAND ON SOMETHING SOFT PLEASE LAND ON SOMETHING SOFT PLEASE LAND ON SOMETHING SOFT

Peter: Y/n! I’m on my way!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

The Vanishing -

Peter: Y/n

Y/n: Oh Peter…

Tony: You’ll be alright, kid.

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

ᴴᵒʷ ᵃᵇᵒᵘᵗ ᵃ ᴾᵗ. ²?

80+ ❤️’s = Endgame version will be made

Peter saving you, to then only regret it..

Peter: You know what? I was actually quite terrified of what might happen once I get there, but now I think I just have more motivation to kick some ass. Ugh, you’re so -

Y/n: Peter! What are you doing here?

Peter: I’m here to help save the world *grunt* obviously!

Before Peter could reach her, Y/n was quick to kick him harshly, sending him falling right back down.

Peter: WHAT WAS THAT FOR?!

Y/n: Sorry Spidey, Iron Man’s orders! We can’t have a teenager’s life in our hands.

Peter: STOP ACTING LIKE I’M THE ONLY YOUNG HERO HERE! YOU’RE ONLY OLDER BY A YEAR!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter trying to give reasons to dislike Y/n -

Peter: You shouldn’t trust her, she’ll only break your heart in unfortunate ways. And she was once one of the bad guys so -

Stephen: You’re the one who had the fling.

Peter: What? How’d you know that?

Stephen: Your metal friend over there.

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter: Y/n! I’m on my way!
